# Documentation Updates

## When Editing Code → Update Docs

| Code Change | Update ARCHITECTURE.md | Update README.md |
|-------------|----------------------|------------------|
| New processor | Module structure | - |
| New CLI option | - | Command options table |
| New phase logic | Three-phase workflow | Features section |
| Config changes | Configuration section | - |
| New output dir | - | Output structure |

## Quick Check
- New file? → Add to ARCHITECTURE.md structure
- User-facing? → Update README.md
- Breaking change? → Update both
